[network]
dns         - Domain Name System related command or information
netstat     - network CONNECTION, ROUTING TABLE, INTERFACE and MULTICAST statistics
ip          - ip, ethtool, ss, netstat commands
curl        - transfer a URL
tcpdump     - dump traffic on a network
dig         - DNS lookup utility


iftop
bmon

18 commands to monitor network bandwith on Linux Server

Overall bandwidth
            nload, bmon, slurm, bwm-ng, cbm, speedometer, netolad

Overall bandwidth (batch style output)
            vnstat, ifstat, dstat, collectl

Bandwidth per socket connection 
            iftop, iptraf, tcptrack, pktstat, netwatch, tarfshow

Bandwidth per process
            nethogs


